---
---

<section id="apply" class="lb-cta relative overflow-hidden bg-primary py-20 text-black lg:py-24">
  <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-5 cta-grid-bg"></div>
  <div class="torn-paper-cta-top"></div>

  <div class="lb-cta-content relative z-10 mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4 pt-8 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="grid gap-12 lg:grid-cols-12 lg:items-start">
      <div class="lg:col-span-5">
        <span class="mb-5 inline-block border border-black bg-white px-4 py-1 font-mono text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] shadow-[4px_4px_0_#000]">Solicitud calificada</span>
        <h2 class="font-display text-4xl font-black leading-none tracking-tight lg:text-6xl">Construyamos una landing que trabaje por tu negocio.</h2>
        <p class="mt-6 text-lg font-medium leading-8 opacity-90">Completá la solicitud y te respondo en menos de 24h si veo una oportunidad real de mejora.</p>

        <div class="mt-8 space-y-4 border-2 border-black bg-black p-5 text-white shadow-[8px_8px_0_rgba(0,0,0,0.25)]">
          <p class="font-display text-xl font-bold">Qué pasa después</p>
          <ol class="space-y-3 text-sm leading-6 text-zinc-300">
            <li><strong class="text-primary">1.</strong> Reviso tu web, oferta y contexto.</li>
            <li><strong class="text-primary">2.</strong> Te respondo en menos de 24h.</li>
            <li><strong class="text-primary">3.</strong> Si hay oportunidad real, coordinamos próximos pasos.</li>
          </ol>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="lg:col-span-7">
        <form class="border-2 border-black bg-white p-6 shadow-[10px_10px_0_#000] sm:p-8" action="#" method="POST">
          <div class="grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2">
            <div>
              <label for="name" class="mb-1 block text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-wider text-gray-700">Nombre</label>
              <input id="name" name="name" type="text" autocomplete="name" required class="w-full border border-gray-300 bg-gray-50 p-3 text-black outline-none transition-colors focus:border-black" placeholder="Tu nombre" />
            </div>
            <div>
              <label for="email" class="mb-1 block text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-wider text-gray-700">Email</label>
              <input id="email" name="email" type="email" autocomplete="email" required class="w-full border border-gray-300 bg-gray-50 p-3 text-black outline-none transition-colors focus:border-black" placeholder="nombre@empresa.com" />
            </div>
            <div class="sm:col-span-2">
              <label for="website" class="mb-1 block text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-wider text-gray-700">Web actual</label>
              <input id="website" name="website" type="url" class="w-full border border-gray-300 bg-gray-50 p-3 text-black outline-none transition-colors focus:border-black" placeholder="https://tuweb.com" />
            </div>
            <div class="sm:col-span-2">
              <label for="offer" class="mb-1 block text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-wider text-gray-700">Qué vendés</label>
              <input id="offer" name="offer" type="text" required class="w-full border border-gray-300 bg-gray-50 p-3 text-black outline-none transition-colors focus:border-black" placeholder="Ej: consultoría, curso, ecommerce, servicio B2B..." />
            </div>
            <div>
              <label for="goal" class="mb-1 block text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-wider text-gray-700">Objetivo principal</label>
              <select id="goal" name="goal" required class="w-full border border-gray-300 bg-gray-50 p-3 text-black outline-none transition-colors focus:border-black">
                <option value="">Seleccionar</option>
                <option>Más consultas calificadas</option>
                <option>Más leads</option>
                <option>Más ventas</option>
                <option>Mejorar conversión de campañas</option>
              </select>
            </div>
            <div>
              <label for="traffic" class="mb-1 block text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-wider text-gray-700">Inversión en tráfico</label>
              <select id="traffic" name="traffic" required class="w-full border border-gray-300 bg-gray-50 p-3 text-black outline-none transition-colors focus:border-black">
                <option value="">Seleccionar</option>
                <option>Ya estoy invirtiendo</option>
                <option>Voy a invertir pronto</option>
                <option>Tengo tráfico orgánico</option>
                <option>No tengo tráfico definido</option>
              </select>
            </div>
            <div class="sm:col-span-2">
              <label for="budget" class="mb-1 block text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-wider text-gray-700">Presupuesto estimado</label>
              <select id="budget" name="budget" required class="w-full border border-gray-300 bg-gray-50 p-3 text-black outline-none transition-colors focus:border-black">
                <option value="">Seleccionar</option>
                <option>USD 1,000 – 2,000</option>
                <option>USD 2,000 – 5,000</option>
                <option>Más de USD 5,000</option>
                <option>Todavía no tengo presupuesto definido</option>
              </select>
            </div>
            <div class="sm:col-span-2">
              <label for="message" class="mb-1 block text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-wider text-gray-700">Mensaje</label>
              <textarea id="message" name="message" rows="4" class="w-full border border-gray-300 bg-gray-50 p-3 text-black outline-none transition-colors focus:border-black" placeholder="Contame contexto, problema actual y qué querés mejorar."></textarea>
            </div>
          </div>

          <button class="mt-6 w-full border-2 border-black bg-black px-6 py-4 font-display text-lg font-black uppercase tracking-wide text-white transition-all hover:bg-white hover:text-black" type="submit">Enviar solicitud</button>
          <p class="mt-4 text-center text-sm font-medium text-gray-600">Sin spam. Sin compromiso. Solo te contacto si puedo ayudarte.</p>
        </form>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
